DIGEST
SB 12 Reengrossed 2026 Regular Session Price
Present law provides for terms used in statutes relative to the Louisiana State Police
Retirement System.
Proposed law adds a definition for "commission" to refer to the State Police Commission and
makes technical changes to clarify existing definitions.
Effective June 30, 2026.
(Amends R.S. 11:1301, 1305(B), 1307.1(B)(2), 1310(A)(1) and (2)(a), 1333, 1334, and
1345.2(1))
